---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const meta = {
  title: 'Bento Review 2025: AI Portfolio Builder for Creators',
  description: 'Bento is an AI-powered portfolio builder for creators. Generate beautiful portfolio sites in minutes. Not a full website builder. Focused on visual portfolios and link-in-bio pages. Free tier available. Pro from $9/month. Best for creators, designers, developers.',
  image: '/og-image.svg',
  keywords: ['Bento review', 'AI portfolio builder', 'Bento pricing', 'portfolio website', 'creator website'],
};
---

<Layout {...meta}>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#F59E0B]/5 to-[#D97706]/5 py-12 sm:py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="text-[10px] sm:text-xs font-black text-[#F59E0B] mb-4 tracking-[0.3em] uppercase">
        AI Tool Review · 2025 Updated
      </p>

      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-black mb-6 leading-tight">
        Bento Review
      </h1>

      <p class="text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl text-gray-700 mb-8">
        Bento is an AI-powered portfolio builder for creators. Give it your social links, work samples, bio - it generates a beautiful portfolio site. Not a full website builder. Focused specifically on portfolios and link-in-bio pages. Fast, simple, designed for people who make things.
      </p>

      <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <p class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">
          Quick answer: Bento is excellent if you need a portfolio or link-in-bio page fast. AI generates the site in seconds. The design is modern and clean. Free tier is generous. Not for complex websites or businesses needing CMS or e-commerce. Use Bento for personal branding, not full business sites.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What It Is -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      What Bento Is (and Isn't)
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">What Bento Does</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Generates portfolios:</strong> AI creates portfolio sites from your links</li>
          <li>• <strong>Link-in-bio pages:</strong> Beautiful alternative to Linktree</li>
          <li>• <strong>Social aggregation:</strong> Pulls content from social platforms</li>
          <li>• <strong>Modern design:</strong> Clean, contemporary aesthetic</li>
          <li>• <strong>Fast setup:</strong> Complete site in minutes</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">What Bento Doesn't Do</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Not a website builder:</strong> Can't build complex multi-page sites</li>
          <li>• <strong>No CMS:</strong> Can't blog or manage content</li>
          <li>• <strong>No e-commerce:</strong> Can't sell products</li>
          <li>• <strong>Limited customization:</strong> Design options are structured</li>
          <li>• <strong>Portfolio focused:</strong> That's all it does, intentionally</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Bento Pricing
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Free (Best for Testing)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Price:</strong> Free forever</li>
          <li>• <strong>Portfolio site:</strong> One portfolio page</li>
          <li>• <strong>Bento branding:</strong> "Made with Bento" on site</li>
          <li>• <strong>Basic features:</strong> All core functionality</li>
          <li>• <strong>Community support:</strong> Help from community</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Value:</strong> Generous for trying Bento and seeing if it fits your needs. Good enough for simple portfolios.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-blue-50 border-2 border-blue-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Pro ($9/month or $90/year)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Everything in Free, plus:</strong></li>
          <li>• <strong>Custom domain:</strong> Use your own domain</li>
          <li>• <strong>No branding:</strong> Remove "Made with Bento"</li>
          <li>• <strong>Analytics:</strong> Visitor analytics and insights</li>
          <li>• <strong>Custom themes:</strong> Access to premium themes</li>
          <li>• <strong>Priority support:</strong> Faster help when needed</li>
          <li>• <strong>Early access:</strong> New features first</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Value:</strong> Fair pricing for what you get. Most serious users will want Pro for custom domain and analytics.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Team ($29/month or $290/year)</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Everything in Pro, plus:</strong></li>
          <li>• <strong>Team collaboration:</strong> Multiple users</li>
          <li>• <strong>Centralized billing:</strong> Manage multiple portfolios</li>
          <li>• <strong>Team analytics:</strong> Aggregate reporting</li>
          <li>• <strong>Dedicated support:</strong> Priority team support</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Value:</strong> For agencies or teams managing multiple creator portfolios.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Features -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Key Features
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">1. AI Portfolio Generation</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Connect your social accounts and Bento pulls your content. AI arranges everything into a cohesive portfolio.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Social integration:</strong> Connect Twitter, Instagram, YouTube, GitHub, Dribbble</li>
          <li>• <strong>Auto-layout:</strong> AI determines optimal arrangement</li>
          <li>• <strong>Content pulling:</strong> Fetches your latest work automatically</li>
          <li>• <strong>Smart curation:</strong> Highlights your best content</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Building a portfolio manually takes hours. Bento does it in minutes. The AI makes decent curation decisions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">2. Link-in-Bio Pages</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Beautiful alternative to Linktree. All your important links in one place. Modern design that matches your portfolio.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Clean design:</strong> Not a boring list of links</li>
          <li>• <strong>Visual cards:</strong> Each link gets visual treatment</li>
          <li>• <strong>Analytics:</strong> Track which links get clicks</li>
          <li>• <strong>Social proof:</strong> Show follower counts and engagement</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Your link-in-bio is often your first impression. Bento makes it professional and memorable.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">3. Modern Templates</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Professionally designed templates optimized for portfolios. Clean, contemporary, creator-focused.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Multiple styles:</strong> Minimal, bold, colorful options</li>
          <li>• <strong>Responsive:</strong> Great on mobile and desktop</li>
          <li>• <strong>Animated:</strong> Subtle micro-interactions and animations</li>
          <li>• <strong>Customizable:</strong> Colors, fonts, spacing</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Design quality matters for portfolios. Bento's templates look professional without effort.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">4. Analytics</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Understand how people interact with your portfolio. Track views, clicks, and engagement.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Visitor tracking:</strong> Know who visits your portfolio</li>
          <li>• <strong>Click tracking:</strong> Which links get the most attention</li>
          <li>• <strong>Referral sources:</strong> Where your traffic comes from</li>
          <li>• <strong>Engagement metrics:</strong> How long people stay</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Data helps you understand what works. Adjust your portfolio based on actual usage patterns.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-purple-50 border-2 border-purple-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">5. Custom Domain</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">Use your own domain on paid plans. Professional branding for your portfolio.</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Easy setup:</strong> Simple DNS configuration</li>
          <li>• <strong>SSL included:</strong> HTTPS security automatic</li>
          <li>• <strong>Subdomains:</strong> Use portfolio.yourdomain.com</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700"><strong>Why it matters:</strong> Your own domain looks more professional. Important for serious creators and job seekers.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Use Cases -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Who Bento Is For
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">✅ Perfect For</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Creators:</strong> YouTubers, podcasters, writers needing portfolios</li>
          <li>• <strong>Designers:</strong> Showcase visual work elegantly</li>
          <li>• <strong>Developers:</strong> Display GitHub repos and projects</li>
          <li>• <strong>Freelancers:</strong> Quick portfolio for client pitches</li>
          <li>• <strong>Job seekers:</strong> Professional online presence</li>
          <li>• <strong>Social-first creators:</strong> Aggregate social content</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">❌ Not For</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Businesses:</strong> Need more than portfolio functionality</li>
          <li>• <strong>Bloggers:</strong> No blogging or CMS features</li>
          <li>• <strong>E-commerce:</strong> Can't sell products</li>
          <li>• <strong>Complex sites:</strong> Multi-page websites aren't supported</li>
          <li>• <strong>Full control:</strong> Want complete design freedom</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pros and Cons -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Pros and Cons
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-green-50 border-2 border-green-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Pros</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Fast setup:</strong> Portfolio in minutes, not hours</li>
          <li>• <strong>Beautiful design:</strong> Modern templates look professional</li>
          <li>• <strong>Free tier:</strong> Generous for testing</li>
          <li>• <strong>Social integration:</strong> Pulls content from platforms automatically</li>
          <li>• <strong>Easy to use:</strong> No technical skills needed</li>
          <li>• <strong>Affordable:</strong> $9/month is reasonable for Pro</li>
          <li>• <strong>Analytics included:</strong> Understand your traffic</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-red-50 border-2 border-red-600 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Cons</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
          <li>• <strong>Limited scope:</strong> Only portfolios, not full websites</li>
          <li>• <strong>Design constraints:</strong> Can't fully customize design</li>
          <li>• <strong>No CMS:</strong> Can't blog or manage content</li>
          <li>• <strong>No e-commerce:</strong> Can't sell products</li>
          <li>• <strong>Platform dependent:</strong> Locked into Bento hosting</li>
          <li>• <strong>Limited pages:</strong> Single page portfolio only</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Alternatives -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-8 text-gray-900">
      Alternatives to Consider
    </h2>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Carrd</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> Simple one-page sites</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> Free or $19/year</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Similar to Bento but more general purpose. Not AI-powered. Cheaper but more manual work.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Linktree</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> Basic link-in-bio pages</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> Free or $6/month</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Focused purely on link lists. Bento is more visually appealing. Linktree is more established.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Webflow</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> Complete design control</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> Free or $14/month</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Full website builder. Can build portfolios but much more complex. Better if you want complete control.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-gray-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-6">
        <h3 class="font-black text-xl mb-4">Framer</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>For:</strong> Modern visual sites</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4"><strong>Price:</strong> Free or $16/month</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700">Visual builder with CMS. Can build portfolios and more. More flexible than Bento but more complex.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Bottom Line -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <div class="bg-white bg-opacity-50 border-2 border-gray-300 rounded-xl p-8">
      <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black mb-6">Bottom Line</h2>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6">Bento fills a specific niche: AI-generated portfolio sites for creators. If that's what you need, it's excellent. If you need a full website, look elsewhere.</p>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6"><strong>Use Bento if:</strong></p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>• You need a portfolio fast</li>
        <li>• You're a creator, designer, or developer</li>
        <li>• You want beautiful design without effort</li>
        <li>• You only need a single page</li>
        <li>• You're okay with limited customization</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6"><strong>Skip Bento if:</strong></p>
      <ul class="space-y-3 mb-6">
        <li>• You need a multi-page website</li>
        <li>• You want to blog or publish content</li>
        <li>• You need e-commerce functionality</li>
        <li>• You require complete design control</li>
        <li>• You're building a business site, not portfolio</li>
      </ul>

      <p class="text-lg text-gray-700"><strong>Bottom line:</strong> Start with the free tier. If Bento does what you need, $9/month is reasonable for Pro. If you outgrow it, migrate to Webflow, Framer, or WordPress for full website capabilities.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Related -->
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12 border-t border-gray-200">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black mb-6 text-gray-900">
      Related Reviews
    </h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <a href="/durable-review" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Durable Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">AI website builder</p>
      </a>
      <a href="/v0-review" class="block bg-gray-50 hover:bg-gray-100 rounded-lg p-6 transition-colors">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">v0.dev Review</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm">AI React code generator</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
